text.tspan: Share of people who completed the initial COVID-19 vaccination
Total number of people who received all doses prescribed by the initial vaccination protocol, divided by the total population
Data source: Official data collated by Our World in Data (2024); World Health Organisation (2025); Population based on various sources
Note: Alternative definitions of a full vaccination, e.g. having been infected with SARS-CoV-2 and having 1 dose of a 2-dose protocol, are
ignored to maximize comparability between countries.
